        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Leviticus 23:26-32",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". The sacrifices prescribed in ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Numbers 29:8-11",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", which are the same as those prescribed for the first day of the seventh month, were to be offered in addition to the sin offerings of atonement prescribed in Leviticus 16 and to the daily burnt offerings. (See Notes on Leviticus 16; ",
        "children": []
      },
