        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "Afflict your souls — ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Yourselves, by abstinence from all delightful things, and by compunction for your sins, and the judgments of God, either deserved by you, or inflicted upon you.",
