    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "On the day of atonement, on the tenth of the seventh month, a similar festal sacrifice was to be offered to the one presented on the seventh new moon's day (a burnt-offering and sin-offering), in addition to the sin-offering of atonement prescribed at ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Leviticus 16",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", and the daily burnt-offerings. For a more minute description of this festival, see at ",
        "children": []
